(162, 1, '2022-06-06 18:52:03', '2022-06-06 15:52:03', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Clarification Text on Processing of Personal Data Received with Forms</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>KVKK AND LIGHTING TEXT<br>Clarification on the Processing of Personal Data Received with Forms</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Doc. Dr. Ünsal Özkuvancı requests some of your personal data (such as your name, surname, password, e-mail address, mobile phone number) by Özkuvancı in order to fulfill its legal obligations arising from the relevant legislation, especially the Personal Data Protection Law No. 6698, and to carry out the processes. Your personal data in question will be processed and stored in an environment that is not accessible to everyone, provided that it is not used outside of the purposes and scope specified in this KVKK and Clarification Text, based on your express consent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Purpose of Processing Personal Data</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Doc. Dr. Personal data before Ünsal Özkuvancı; planning and execution of commercial activities, providing information to authorized institutions and organizations based on the legislation, resolving consumer complaints on issues that are not directly provided by us and which are not within our field of expertise, sending commercial electronic messages if you give your explicit consent, Doc. Dr. Ünsal Özkuvancı is obliged to comply with the law for the purpose of planning and executing the necessary audit activities to ensure that they are carried out in accordance with the procedures and relevant legislation, planning and executing corporate sustainability activities, carrying out studies to protect the reputation of our company, managing the request and complaint processes, planning and executing corporate governance and communication activities. related to the rules of honesty and the purpose for which they are processed, It will be processed in accordance with the principles of limited and measured storage, as stipulated in the relevant legislation or for the period required for the purpose for which they are processed. Your personal data can be obtained, saved, stored, preserved, changed, rearranged, etc., in whole or in part, by automatic or non-automatic means. can be processed through transactions. The collected information is never shared with third parties without your knowledge or otherwise, and is not used for commercial purposes or sold for any reason other than activity. can be processed through transactions. The collected information is never shared with third parties without your knowledge or otherwise, and is not used for commercial purposes or sold for any reason other than activity. can be processed through transactions. The collected information is never shared with third parties without your knowledge or otherwise, and is not used for commercial purposes or sold for any reason other than activity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Transfer of Personal Data</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It may be shared with legally authorized public and/or private law legal entities and persons or organizations permitted or required by other legislation provisions, limited to the purpose requested within its legal authority, with official authorities upon the request of official authorities. Your personal data may be transferred to third parties without your explicit consent in accordance with Articles 5 and 8 of the Personal Data Protection Law.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Collection Method of Personal Data</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your personal data may be collected in written, oral or electronic form through our website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Deletion, Destruction or Anonymization of Personal Data</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pursuant to Article 7 of the KVK Law, although the personal data has been processed in accordance with the relevant legislation, in the event that the reasons for the processing are no longer valid, the personal data will be processed ex officio or upon the request of the personal data owner. Dr. It is deleted, destroyed or anonymized by Ünsal Özkuvancı. The procedures and principles regarding this matter will be fulfilled in accordance with the KVK Law and the Regulation on the Deletion, Destruction or Anonymization of Personal Data published in the Official Gazette dated 28.10.2017 and numbered 30224. Personal data is deleted, destroyed or anonymized within 3 months following the date of our obligation to delete, destroy or anonymize personal data. When you request the deletion or destruction of your personal data by applying to our company;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>a) If all the conditions for processing personal data have disappeared; Your personal data subject to the request is deleted, destroyed or anonymized. Your request will be finalized within 30 days at the latest and you will be informed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>b) If all the conditions for processing personal data have been removed and the personal data subject to the request has been transferred to third parties, it notifies the third parties; It is ensured that the necessary actions are taken within the scope of the regulation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>c) If all the conditions for processing personal data have not been eliminated, your request may be rejected by explaining the reason in accordance with the third paragraph of Article 13 of the KVK Law and the rejection will be notified to you in writing or electronically within 30 days at the latest.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your Rights Arising from the Law on the Protection of Personal Data</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to Article 11 of the Law, customers as personal data owners;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>– Learning whether personal data is processed or not,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>– Requesting information on personal data if it has been processed,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>– To learn the purpose of processing personal data and whether they are used in accordance with its purpose,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>– Knowing the third parties to whom personal data is transferred in the country or abroad,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>– Requesting correction of personal data if it is incomplete or incorrectly processed,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>– Requesting the deletion, anonymization or destruction of personal data,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>– Requesting notification to third parties in case of correction, deletion, anonymization or destruction,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>– Objecting to the emergence of a result against the person himself by analyzing the processed data exclusively through automated systems,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>– In case of damage due to unlawful processing of their personal data, they have the right to demand the compensation of the damage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Non-personal information is information that you cannot personally identify. This information can be used for any purpose and can be shared with third parties without their consent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'KVKK ve Aydınlatma Metni', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kvkk-ve-aydinlatma-metni', '', '', '2022-06-06 18:52:03', '2022-06-06 15:52:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/docunsal/?page_id=162', 0, 'page', '', 0),
